
Django devel setup
------------------

Mathias:

$ export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:/home/nis/monnerville/spica2
$ django-admin.py runserver \
 	--settings=settings_dev_mat \
	--pythonpath=/home/nis/monnerville/spica2/terapix \
	--adminmedia=/home/nis/monnerville/spica2/terapix/media \
	194.57.221.40:8000 &

